description:
This week Adam Salandra stops by to talk about an episode of Real Housewives of Orange County that Danny says was "painful to watch" where the girls went golfing. They also chat about the amazing TV that is Real Housewives of Dallas, look back on fallen Housewives of yesteryear, and break down a photo of Vicki Gunvalson, Jill Zarin, Cynthia Bailey, and P*tti St*nger.


*To support this podcast and for bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
